What is Python? What are the ways to install python in PC?
Python is an interpreted , high-level programmimg language, Open source so its source code is available in its website and speakable english like commands!!!

Installation ways:-
1. Download the installation package from Python.org
2. Download IDE based python which has in-built libraries such as Anaconda distribution(JupyterNotebook, Spyder which has several in-built libraries
3. Various other IDEs are available.

What are the Code Environments? and its Types
A code environment is a platform that consists of equipment that can be used for scripting codes, execution, developing, or testing the software.
Environments are independent
There are 3 types of environments
1.Text Editors
2.Integrated Development Environment
3. Notebook Environment
